{
  "stem": "7546.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We knew that by their behavior, by their nonchalance, by their uniforms, and by-- by the orders that they were giving us how to handle the luggage.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "The scene was really macabre.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "There's-- there no other explanation I could give you of-- of that exiting of these people.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Every one of them was a high-ranking officer.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Their wives were dressed to kill.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And then I didn't know what a mink coat was, but now I realize some of them had mink coats, broad tails, [? karakul, ?] expensive [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And they all came.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "They got off the train, and they stood in line, like soldiers really should.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And their wives stood separately, and they stood separately.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And we are unloading the luggage and putting the luggage, separately, in a very even line, that they should be able to find their luggage.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now, he was not a German.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I-- to this day I don't know whether he was-- he could have been Latvian, Lithuanian, or Ukrainian.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And that German picks up some kind of rubber club in his hand and smacked that man across the face, and his teeth actually flew in the air.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And he almost fell, but before he fell, he gave him another shot from the other end.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, we didn't!",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We didn't!",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They came so well dressed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The ladies, made up, manicured fingers, beautiful hairdos, hats, fur coats.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I said before, fur coats!",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they were dressed in high-ranking German uniforms and medals that wouldn't fit on my chest.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Every one of them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then more German soldiers came, and they started hitting every one of them.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They were hitting them without any pity.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Now, this story starts, the heartbreaking story.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "In the Lodz ghetto, we only had outhouses.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
